snippet.textDisplay: 5:48 Amit Trivedi's triumphant crescendos! 🔥 and this one feels right up there with Azaadiyan! @MILIofficialmusic 's vocals kick in with a burst of energy every single time, Mame Khan's earthy vocals & Arshad Khan's israj keep it rooted, Thomson Andrews deserves a special mention.. but personally, the backing vox group with one of the most impactful chorus which comes to mind remains my favorite aspect of this underrated masterpiece ❤

snippet.textDisplay: Amit Trivedi performed live with his band a while back in Kolkata. They finished their set and asked the crowd for any recommendations. I and a couple of my friends shouted for "Badri Badariya" near the stage. He heard us, but didn't have the sokf prepared. But, he searched the song, three people uses the same device and they performed this banger. Live! 😍
snippet.textOriginal: Amit Trivedi performed live with his band a while back in Kolkata. They finished their set and asked the crowd for any recommendations. I and a couple of my friends shouted for "Badri Badariya" near the stage. He heard us, but didn't have the sokf prepared. But, he searched the song, three people uses the same device and they performed this banger. Live! 😍
